title: Unicorn tech company that made a grand Tampa entrance shuts down - St Pete Catalyst
content: Unicorn tech company that made a grand Tampa entrance shuts down  St Pete Catalyst
description: The San Fransisco-based fintech startup Fast, which celebrated the opening of its Tampa East Coast hub last year, is closing.   The startup that provides an online checkout platform took to Twitter on Tuesday to announce its closure.  "After making great strides on our mission of making [sic] buying and selling frictionless for everyone, we have [...]
